shortdesc Simple macros supporting abreviations for Plain and LaTeX
longdesc The package provides some simple macros to support
longdesc abbreviations in Plain TeX or LaTeX. It allows writing (e.g.)
longdesc \<TEX> instead of \TeX, hence frees users from having to escape
longdesc space after parameterless macros.
